<p>Pick and choose your ideal combination of metrics, or use a pre-existing template. <a href="https://help.hootsuite.com/hc/en-us/articles/217144738-Export-or-schedule-exports-of-analytics-data">Export right away in the format of your choice</a>, or schedule them for automated email delivery. </p>
