<p>TikTok recommends posting <a href="https://www.tiktok.com/business/en/blog/tiktok-creative-ultimate-guide">minimum once a day</a> and up to four times a day for best results. Once a day doesn’t sound like a lot until you realize that’s basically conceptualizing, scripting, shooting and editing what used to be a TV commercial every single day.</p>
<p>For Facebook, <a href="https://blog.hootsuite.com/facebook-algorithm/">recency is a top algorithm factor</a>. Newer posts are always given more weight, even when combined with other ranking factors. It’s especially important to know when your target audience is on Facebook and post accordingly.</p>
<p>For more info on algorithms, check out our detailed posts for each social platform:</p>
<ul>
